PayuMoney Integration By Using Laravel

1.make PayumoneyController name of controller 
2.make routing for the connection to front and back ang also get 
payment response
3.make 2 view pages such as index.blade.php and response.blade.php
4.Inside index.blade.php there need csrf token as a form field so 
be careful with casf problem in this page
5. After successfull of payment, the response url make some problem, this
problem arise just for csrf. So for that you need to declare your response 
routing into your VerifyCsrfToken.php(app\http\Middleware\)